article.headline: Utah Valley defeats Abilene Christian 74-45
article.description: — Ethan Potter had 20 points in Utah Valley's 74-45 win over Abilene Christian on Saturday night.
article.story: OREM, Utah -- — Ethan Potter had 20 points in Utah Valley's 74-45 win over Abilene Christian on Saturday night. Potter added eight rebounds and three steals for the Wolverines (10-14, 5-8 Western Athletic Conference). Trevin Dorius scored 12 points and added eight rebounds and three blocks. Jaden McClanahan was 4 of 7 shooting (3 for 4 from 3-point range) to finish with 11 points. The Wildcats (8-15, 3-9) were led in scoring by Ali Abdou Dibba, who finished with 17 points and three steals. Hunter Jack Madden added 11 points for Abilene Christian. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
